22 SECTION 4. EXTRA HELP. There is hereby authorized, for the Department
23 of Energy and Environment - Division of Environmental Quality for the 2025-
24 2026 fiscal year, the following maximum number of part-time or temporary
25 employees, to be known as "Extra Help", payable from funds appropriated
26 herein for such purposes: seventy (70) temporary or part-time employees, when
27 needed, at rates of pay not to exceed those provided in the Uniform
28 Classification and Compensation Act, or its successor, or this act for the
29 appropriate classification.
