19 SECTION 39. SPECIAL LANGUAGE. NOT TO BE INCORPORATED INTO THE ARKANSAS
20 CODE NOR PUBLISHED SEPARATELY AS SPECIAL, LOCAL AND TEMPORARY LAW. LANDFILL
21 POST-CLOSURE CLEAN UP RESTRICTIONS. Any expenditures in excess of $2,000,000
22 per site from the Landfill Post-Closure Trust Fund, as appropriated in the
23 Contractual Services line item of the Landfill Post-Closure Program
24 appropriation section, for corrective action to remedy environmental impacts
25 of closed disposal sites previously operated as a landfill pursuant to state
26 law, shall be subject to review and approval by the Arkansas Pollution
27 Control and Ecology Commission after addressing corrective actions needed to
28 address environmental impacts from permitted landfills closed properly.
29 The provisions of this section shall be in effect only from July 1, 2024
30 2025 through June 30, 2025 2026.
